+ *	ignored.
+ * @tdcv_max: Transmitter Delay Compensation Value maximum value. If
+ *	the controller does not support manual mode for tdcv
+ *	(c.f. flag CAN_CTRLMODE_TDC_MANUAL) then this value is
+ *	ignored.
